            <ab>OF REV. N. C. BURT DD</ab>
            <ab>U.S.A.</ab>
            <ab>WHO DEPARTED THIS LIFE IN THIS CITY</ab>
            <ab>MARCH 4th 1870</ab>
            <ab>AGED 49 YEARS</ab>
            <ab/>
            <ab>HE WAS NOT, FOR GOD TOOK HIM</ab>
            <ab/>
            <ab rend="Alignl">FOR IF WE BELIEVE JESUS DIED AND ROSE</ab>
            <ab rend="Alignl">AGAIN, EVEN SO THEM ALSO WHICH SLEEP IN</ab>
            <ab rend="Alignl">JESUS WILL GOD BRING WITH THEM</ab>
